1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:06,331
AI fluency is not measured by prompt complexity, daily usage, or how quickly you accept an answer.

2
00:00:06,281 --> 00:00:10,394
It is the quality of the decisions that connect your intent to a real outcome.

3
00:00:10,394 --> 00:00:15,211
First, Delegation decides whether, where, and how AI should participate.

4
00:00:15,211 --> 00:00:20,798
Second, Description makes the goal, context, constraints, and evidence explicit.

5
00:00:20,798 --> 00:00:25,951
Third, Discernment tests the output, while Diligence controls and verifies its use.

6
00:00:25,951 --> 00:00:29,951
For your next task, use the 4D card before execution.

7
00:00:29,951 --> 00:00:36,730
Repair every zero, keep the acceptance test visible, and let evidence determine whether the AI receives more authority.

8
00:00:36,730 --> 00:00:38,596
The models will change.

9
00:00:38,596 --> 00:00:44,692
The need to choose the right work, describe it clearly, judge results, and own consequences will remain.

10
00:00:44,692 --> 00:00:48,461
Those are the skills that make stronger AI genuinely useful.

11
00:00:48,461 --> 00:00:50,307
Follow Tiny Agent.

12
00:00:50,307 --> 00:00:53,346
Tiny Agent helps you get better at using AI.
